oups... organizations in which your reputation and abilities count more than your guild tag.<br>
<br>
Aye, HU still holds MUSHes and mid level XP groups/raids every week.  None of our members use anon or roleplay so that people can find us when they require assistance.  That doesn't mean I am going to leave discos in Sebilis to come SoW and invis you at portal in DL but I won't refuse a reasonable request and may even ninja-buff your twink for no reason whatsoever. <p><a href="http://216.118.107.63/SIGS/juror.jpg" target="_blank">
